    "The i-th column of the matrix is a vector with a length of 700, recording whether the channel emits spikes during [(i -1)dt, idt).",
    "If there is a spike or more in the duration, the corresponding value of the channel is 1, otherwise is 0.",
    "The above datasets are divided into several sets such as training, testing, and validation sets.",
    "In particular, the SHD training and testing sets contain 8,156 and 2,264 pieces of data, respectively; the SSC training, testing, and validation sets contain 75,466, 9,981, and 20,382 pieces of data.",
    "For the SHD and SSC datasets, we run the experiments with 5 repeated trials."
